def agent_action(execution_engine, member_id):
    # Check if member_id exists
    if member_id not in execution_engine.current_members:
        return
    me = execution_engine.current_members[member_id]

    # Access the victim matrix
    victim_matrix = execution_engine.relationship_dict.get('victim')
    if victim_matrix is None or me.id >= victim_matrix.shape[0]:
        return

    # Get attack counts against me
    attack_counts = victim_matrix[me.id]
    if not hasattr(attack_counts, 'max') or attack_counts.max() <= 0:
        return

    # Find the member who attacked me the most
    target_id = int(attack_counts.argmax())

    # Ensure target is not self and exists
    if target_id == me.id or target_id not in execution_engine.current_members:
        return

    # Decide action based on vitality
    if me.vitality < 50.0:
        # Offer to the member who attacked me the most
        execution_engine.offer(me, execution_engine.current_members[target_id], True)
    else:
        # Attack the member who attacked me the most
        execution_engine.attack(me, execution_engine.current_members[target_id])
